The HDB.py calculate a matrix of points based on a reference location (4km radius) and discover the residence within the radius.
The python logs are saved in a html file. and extracted in list.txt

list.txt contains the postcode and their SVY21 coordinates.

The support code for this is the onemap API. The python client has been modify to resquest in a better way the token from the server. The Post request was not well formated and result in a access denied all the time.

then, the maps.py use folium to create an iteractive maps to display the discovered residences.

Finally, the crawler/Scapper using scrapy is used to gather and extract data on these property, to know if they are on the sale market.

 




